使用分支控制，可以在不影响主分支的情况下，推进翻译的改进。: Using branch control, it is possible to advance the improvement of translation without affecting the main branch.
如果源字符串或标识符（key）被修改（匹配重复的标准），则会认为该字符串已被删除: If the source string or identifier (key) is modified (matching the duplicate criteria), then it will be considered that the string has been deleted/added (the old one is deleted and the new one is added).
在分支上修改的翻译将被合并在一起（自己的和共享的），并保留批准和投票。: Translations modified on the branch will be merged together (own and shared), and approvals and votes will be retained.
合并摘要仅包括源字符串的统计信息。字符串的翻译、投票和批准也将被合并。: The merged summary only includes the statistical information of the source string. The translation, voting and approval of the string will also be merged.
合并后删除分支: Merge and then delete the branch
以 . 作为分隔符转换为对象: Convert to an object using . as a separator.
使用通配符选择器（“**”、“*”、“?”、“[set]”、“\\\\”等）处理: Use wildcard selectors ("**", "*", "?", "[set]", "\\", etc.) to handle multiple branches.
邀请你加入翻译项目: You are invited to join the translation project.
多个邮箱请使用英文,隔开: Multiple email addresses should be separated by commas.
将作为邮件的附加消息进行发送。: Will be sent as an additional message in the email.
对整个项目拥有无限的控制权: Having unlimited control over the entire project.
可以翻译内容并对现有翻译进行投票: You can translate content and vote on existing translations.
可以翻译和校对内容: Can translate and proofread the content
邀请链接已复制: The invitation link has been copied.
暂无链接: No links available at the moment.
撤销后，该邀请链接将失效，是否继续？: After revocation, the invitation link will become invalid, would you like to proceed?
唯一标识只能是小写字母和-，小写字母开头: The unique identifier can only consist of lowercase letters and hyphens, starting with a lowercase letter.
删除该翻译项目，所以的翻译数据将无法使用，是否继续？: Delete the translation project, all translation data will be unusable, continue?
删除项目将永久删除与该项目关联的所有资源，包括上传的文件、翻译、审批等。删除的项: Deleting a project will permanently delete all resources associated with that project, including uploaded files, translations, approvals, etc. Deleted projects cannot be recovered!
成功后不关闭窗口: Do not close the window after success
请输入原始语言词条: Please enter the original language term.
是否批准改翻译作为有效结果: Whether to approve the translation as a valid result
是否撤销此翻译的有效结果: Whether to revoke the valid result of this translation
名称只能是小写字母、符号：. -，小写字母开头: The name can only be lowercase letters, symbols:., -, and start with a lowercase letter
请输入完整的匹配规则: Please enter the complete matching rule
唯一标识不能为空: The unique identifier cannot be empty.
请检查邮箱格式是否正常: Please check whether the mailbox format is normal.
唯一标识只能是小写字母、数字和-，小写字母开头: The unique identifier can only be lowercase letters, numbers and -, starting with a lowercase letter
